Playing Whip It
Playing 9 to 5
Stopped!
Playing Jessie's Girl
Playing Whip It
Playing 9 to 5
Stopped!
```

## Type assertions

* If you have a value with an interface type, you can only call methods included in that interface.
* This is true even if the concrete value has that method!

## Type assertions

``` go
